# read_theory_cluster.md

## File
utils/theory-cluster/theory_cluster.py

---

## 1. Purpose

Generate structured theory outputs per Data Governance domain by:

- Reading domain YAML definitions (decision_tree + action_catalog)
- Extracting authoritative PDF excerpts
- Grounding content using framework references
- Generating structured prescriptive outputs via OpenAI
- Writing per-domain cluster outputs with caching and cost control

This script is the foundational generation layer of the DOMMx Theory Stack.

---

## 2. Architecture Overview

High-level flow:

flow.yaml
   ↓
Domain YAMLs (decision_tree + action_catalog)
   ↓
Flatten into structured rows
   ↓
Extract topics and PDF excerpts (cached)
   ↓
OpenAI generation (parallel, batched)
   ↓
Per-domain cluster JSON output

---

